WEBVTT

00:39.020 --> 00:40.360
May I be like the stars

00:40.380 --> 00:41.580
and you like the moon.

00:42.390 --> 00:43.880
As long as the world remains,

00:44.710 --> 00:46.010
so shall we.

01:01.720 --> 01:04.010
I only wish to stay with the one I love,

01:04.430 --> 01:06.370
watching every sunrise and sunset.

01:07.640 --> 01:09.660
I want to be with you forever.

01:13.620 --> 01:15.010
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

01:15.640 --> 01:17.480
You and she are ultimately different.

01:37.970 --> 01:39.600
Have you ever

01:40.220 --> 01:41.789
truly cared for me?

01:44.440 --> 01:45.250
No.

01:45.660 --> 01:46.360
Never.

01:54.650 --> 01:57.720
In this life and the next, through all lifetimes…

02:02.150 --> 02:03.310
May we live and die together,

02:04.400 --> 02:06.040
and share life and death as one.

02:41.710 --> 02:45.710
[Moonlight Mystique]

02:46.310 --> 02:49.910
[Episode 7]

02:50.750 --> 02:51.960
Hurry up!

02:53.430 --> 02:54.150
Hurry!

03:00.230 --> 03:02.650
Can you be faster?

03:03.070 --> 03:04.550
-Hurry up!
-So annoying.

03:04.570 --> 03:05.180
Full of nonsense.

03:05.240 --> 03:06.520
Hurry!

03:18.480 --> 03:19.170
Wait.

03:19.730 --> 03:21.290
What does running

03:21.310 --> 03:23.110
have to do with cultivating?

03:23.380 --> 03:24.630
Of course it does.

03:24.680 --> 03:26.310
Have you forgotten what I told you yesterday?

03:26.310 --> 03:27.540
What's the most important thing

03:27.560 --> 03:28.860
in a duel?

03:30.150 --> 03:32.690
You're not trying to teach me how to escape, are you?

03:34.690 --> 03:36.010
You're very smart.

03:36.030 --> 03:37.040
What you're learning today

03:37.070 --> 03:38.140
is the

03:38.190 --> 03:38.870
Turtle

03:38.900 --> 03:39.650
Running

03:39.670 --> 03:40.829
Technique.

03:42.650 --> 03:44.020
Yesterday you taught me to play dead,

03:44.050 --> 03:45.230
and today you're teaching me to escape.

03:45.290 --> 03:46.520
Turtle, don't forget

03:46.550 --> 03:48.880
you promised Fan Yue to teach me Eternal skills.

03:48.910 --> 03:50.220
If you keep messing with me,

03:50.240 --> 03:51.950
I'll call that devil here right now.

03:52.560 --> 03:53.840
My good disciple.

03:53.870 --> 03:55.520
Don't rush.

03:55.560 --> 03:57.670
After all, I'm a 1000-year-old spirit turtle.

03:57.690 --> 04:00.630
When teaching, I've got to put on some airs, right?

04:00.660 --> 04:02.470
I officially inform you

04:02.490 --> 04:04.640
that you have passed all of my tests.

04:04.670 --> 04:05.710
From today on,

04:05.750 --> 04:06.640
I will teach you

04:06.660 --> 04:07.870
the real

04:08.760 --> 04:10.400
skills.

04:11.490 --> 04:12.380
Really?

04:15.880 --> 04:17.670
Are these the real skills you mentioned?

04:19.130 --> 04:21.320
My signature skills

04:21.339 --> 04:23.150
are divination and alchemy.

04:21.970 --> 04:22.730
[Golden Elixir Scripture] [Zifu Pill Formula]

04:22.750 --> 04:24.390
[Golden Elixir Scripture]

04:23.180 --> 04:24.890
Today, I'll teach you,

04:24.950 --> 04:26.680
without holding anything back.

04:29.470 --> 04:31.680
Don't just pull out that little seashell every time.

04:31.680 --> 04:32.510
I'm telling you,

04:32.510 --> 04:35.360
I'm really not messing with you this time.

04:35.360 --> 04:36.240
They really are

04:36.240 --> 04:37.390
my signature skills.

04:37.390 --> 04:39.080
He knows what I want.

04:39.100 --> 04:40.300
I want to be stronger.

04:40.330 --> 04:41.890
What does he want me to learn from you?

04:41.909 --> 04:42.790
Divination?

04:42.830 --> 04:44.040
Or alchemy?

04:44.060 --> 04:46.330
These can't make me stronger.

04:46.360 --> 04:48.470
He doesn't really want to help me,

04:48.490 --> 04:49.530
and neither do you.

04:49.940 --> 04:51.090
Stop right there!

04:52.360 --> 04:54.490
No one is born the strongest.

04:54.950 --> 04:56.120
If you can't even protect yourself,

04:56.140 --> 04:58.580
how can you live long enough to grow stronger?

05:06.130 --> 05:06.900
You can't get fat

05:06.930 --> 05:08.300
by eating one bite.

05:08.350 --> 05:10.310
You can't reach the sky in one step.

05:10.590 --> 05:11.590
If you aim unreasonably high

05:11.610 --> 05:12.800
and rush things,

05:12.830 --> 05:14.520
the more you practice, the worse you'll get,

05:14.560 --> 05:15.930
and the further you'll stray from the path.

05:15.960 --> 05:16.690
To grow stronger,

05:16.710 --> 05:18.640
it's not just about strength.

05:18.670 --> 05:20.110
It's also about mindset.

05:20.130 --> 05:21.760
If you want to learn properly,

05:21.790 --> 05:22.720
stay

05:22.740 --> 05:24.920
and start from the basics.

05:24.950 --> 05:26.150
If you don't want to learn,

05:26.170 --> 05:27.620
you can grab that little seashell

05:27.650 --> 05:28.650
and call Fan Yue over

05:28.670 --> 05:30.080
to take you back right now.

05:30.110 --> 05:32.220
At worst, I'll just get beaten by him again.

05:32.670 --> 05:33.700
But you...

05:34.000 --> 05:34.800
will never

05:34.800 --> 05:36.159
amount to anything.

05:39.390 --> 05:41.520
Weren't you giving me the turtle shell and the medicine book?

05:42.240 --> 05:43.720
Why did you take them away?

05:46.030 --> 05:46.860
So,

05:46.880 --> 05:48.320
where do we start,

05:48.350 --> 05:49.110
Master?

05:52.400 --> 05:53.320
What

05:53.340 --> 05:54.590
did you just call me?

05:55.170 --> 05:56.510
Master.

06:02.630 --> 06:03.270
Since

06:03.270 --> 06:04.820
you've called me Master,

06:04.900 --> 06:05.580
today,

06:05.630 --> 06:06.460
we should

06:06.490 --> 06:07.690
set a rule.

06:07.710 --> 06:08.540
What rule?

06:08.570 --> 06:09.420
Just tell me.

06:10.930 --> 06:11.890
To become my disciple,

06:12.190 --> 06:13.630
you need to pay first.

06:15.540 --> 06:17.250
It's not what I want either.

06:17.270 --> 06:20.350
I'm just staying here temporarily in Lanling,

06:20.380 --> 06:22.620
and I have to pay for accommodation every month.

06:22.640 --> 06:24.520
Otherwise, they would've kicked me out long ago.

06:24.550 --> 06:26.400
They are so stingy.

06:26.420 --> 06:27.620
Why are you still staying here?

06:27.650 --> 06:28.800
Do you think I want

06:28.830 --> 06:30.800
to be exploited by those old fossils?

06:30.800 --> 06:32.040
I've been making elixirs every day,

06:32.040 --> 06:32.680
and it...

06:32.680 --> 06:34.810
and it has made my turtle shell almost crack.

06:34.830 --> 06:37.220
But I'm the only 1000-year-old spirit turtle

06:37.250 --> 06:40.210
in the whole Eastern Continent.

06:40.230 --> 06:42.220
Everyone knows I'm skilled in divination,

06:42.280 --> 06:45.960
and everyone wants to capture me to predict the future for them.

06:45.990 --> 06:47.790
In this vast world,

06:47.810 --> 06:49.080
only Lanling

06:49.110 --> 06:50.750
can protect

06:50.770 --> 06:53.450
my turtle body!

06:56.880 --> 06:58.310
It's it.

06:58.330 --> 06:59.460
There are four steps:

06:59.490 --> 07:00.970
look, smell, touch, and taste.

07:00.990 --> 07:03.600
These are the ways to identify medicinal herbs.

07:03.630 --> 07:05.300
My disciple, as the saying goes,

07:05.320 --> 07:07.560
make the most of what's around you.

07:07.590 --> 07:08.960
Since you've come to this mountain,

07:09.000 --> 07:10.800
you should learn to make use of what others consider useless.

07:10.800 --> 07:12.850
What's the effect of the old tree bark?

07:12.870 --> 07:13.750
It clears heat and disperses blood stasis.

07:13.800 --> 07:14.730
Smart!

07:14.750 --> 07:15.670
Let's go.

07:21.210 --> 07:22.750
How do you make it?

07:23.710 --> 07:24.800
Turn up the heat.

07:25.480 --> 07:27.070
Don't underestimate this alchemy furnace.

07:27.070 --> 07:29.120
It's older than me.

07:29.120 --> 07:31.160
It was forged from meteoric iron that fell from the sky.

07:33.420 --> 07:35.159
Have you understood?

07:35.159 --> 07:36.360
Good.

07:38.090 --> 07:39.140
Wait.

08:08.530 --> 08:09.620
Can you understand it?

08:09.650 --> 08:10.850
I can.

08:10.880 --> 08:12.030
What does the letter say?

08:12.800 --> 08:14.120
They also refused to come.

08:16.040 --> 08:17.310
Among the 72 Sects,

08:17.310 --> 08:19.160
except for Kunlun Sect and the Wuliang Sect,

08:19.160 --> 08:20.680
none are willing to start a war.

08:20.680 --> 08:23.070
Then how can we conquer the Cold Spring Palace?

08:23.710 --> 08:24.960
Be gentle.

08:25.280 --> 08:26.810
This table was just repaired.

08:26.830 --> 08:27.420
I know.

08:27.450 --> 08:28.570
I held back my strength.

08:29.040 --> 08:30.680
The 72 Sects

08:30.680 --> 08:32.240
each have their own philosophy.

08:32.870 --> 08:34.419
Some seek worldly engagement,

08:34.440 --> 08:35.929
some are reclusive;

08:35.460 --> 08:39.070
[When the Lanling Sect and others discuss the matter of the conquest, our sect will definitely spare no effort]

08:35.460 --> 08:39.070
[Our sect fully agrees and is willing to work together to discuss the strategy for the conquest]

08:35.960 --> 08:38.490
some value culture, some value martial arts;

08:38.520 --> 08:40.610
some are radical, some are conservative.

08:40.630 --> 08:43.820
The different philosophies lead to disagreements.

08:43.850 --> 08:46.020
Since the truce between the Eternals Race and the Demon Race 100 years ago,

08:46.040 --> 08:48.390
the Human Race has been living in peace.

08:48.410 --> 08:51.180
It's understandable that the Eternals

08:51.210 --> 08:52.710
don't want to break this peace.

08:52.730 --> 08:53.870
Sect Leader, since you know this,

08:53.870 --> 08:55.000
why did you send letters to them?

08:55.380 --> 08:56.860
I thought that

08:56.890 --> 08:59.770
even if some sects don't like war,

08:59.790 --> 09:02.310
among the 72 sects,

09:02.360 --> 09:03.480
there would still be at least

09:03.750 --> 09:06.060
30% supporting it.

09:06.130 --> 09:07.890
But I didn't expect that

09:07.920 --> 09:09.550
I couldn't find even three sects.

09:10.520 --> 09:11.670
As you all know,

09:12.330 --> 09:16.360
these sects are spread across the Eastern Continent.

09:16.390 --> 09:17.960
It was...

09:19.220 --> 09:21.190
It was exhausting.

09:22.000 --> 09:23.440
But that's not the main problem.

09:23.440 --> 09:24.550
The real problem is that

09:24.550 --> 09:25.870
we spent a lot of money

09:25.870 --> 09:27.720
from the treasury to send the letters this time.

09:28.300 --> 09:30.430
It's becoming increasingly empty.

09:31.580 --> 09:33.780
You should stop using the term "treasury."

09:33.860 --> 09:35.300
Otherwise,

09:35.330 --> 09:36.960
people will think we're rich.

09:37.100 --> 09:39.100
Well, why don't you start some new business?

09:39.150 --> 09:39.980
Back then,

09:40.000 --> 09:42.080
when Chong Zhao was running that steamed bun stall,

09:42.520 --> 09:44.090
he made quite a lot of money.

09:44.120 --> 09:45.070
Yes.

09:45.610 --> 09:47.130
Speaking of Chong Zhao,

09:47.150 --> 09:48.420
he's already been punished

09:48.450 --> 09:49.810
and has completed his self-reflection.

09:49.870 --> 09:51.600
I think it's time to let him back.

09:51.630 --> 09:53.700
Although he can no longer serve as an Eternal Envoy,

09:53.720 --> 09:54.930
he is, after all,

09:54.960 --> 09:56.830
the head disciple of Lanling Sect.

09:56.850 --> 09:58.730
We can't just let him stay on that mountain forever.

10:04.870 --> 10:05.950
Master Turtle!

10:05.970 --> 10:06.850
Master Turtle!

10:06.960 --> 10:08.030
Master Turtle!

10:08.030 --> 10:08.790
Master Turtle, are you there?

10:08.790 --> 10:12.240
I'll be out in a minute! Wait for me in the yard!

10:12.240 --> 10:13.740
Hurry up and find a place to hide.

10:14.030 --> 10:15.270
Coming!

10:16.550 --> 10:17.550
Master Turtle!

10:17.580 --> 10:18.360
Master Turtle!

10:18.360 --> 10:21.480
Coming!

10:21.480 --> 10:23.270
I'm here.

10:25.350 --> 10:27.360
-Thank you, Master Turtle.
-Thank you, Master Turtle.

10:27.360 --> 10:28.670
There's no need.

10:29.290 --> 10:30.930
What's going on lately?

10:30.960 --> 10:33.470
Why do you suddenly need such a large amount of elixirs?

10:33.510 --> 10:34.390
Well,

10:34.410 --> 10:35.960
it's because of Chong Zhao.

10:35.990 --> 10:36.870
They all say that Chong Zhao

10:36.910 --> 10:39.190
is a once-in-a-century genius in Lanling

10:39.220 --> 10:40.500
with limitless potential.

10:40.520 --> 10:42.470
But now he has been given 300 lashes

10:42.500 --> 10:43.930
and sent to Heart-guarding Cliff.

10:43.960 --> 10:45.470
However, with him gone,

10:45.490 --> 10:47.820
the position of the Eternal Envoy in Ning'an City is now vacant.

10:47.850 --> 10:49.520
The Sect Leader said there will be a martial arts competition,

10:49.540 --> 10:50.350
and the winner

10:50.380 --> 10:51.600
will become the new Eternal Envoy.

10:52.410 --> 10:54.360
We expend spiritual power during training,

10:54.390 --> 10:55.720
so we came to ask you

10:55.720 --> 10:57.150
for some elixirs to replenish it.

10:57.150 --> 10:58.030
Chong Zhao

10:58.030 --> 10:59.650
is the Sect Leader's direct disciple.

10:59.680 --> 11:00.920
How did he end up like this?

11:00.960 --> 11:01.750
Well,

11:01.750 --> 11:02.930
he brought it upon himself.

11:02.960 --> 11:04.440
If he had had no other choices,

11:04.460 --> 11:05.580
it would have been acceptable.

11:05.630 --> 11:07.070
But to save someone, he delayed reporting

11:07.090 --> 11:08.900
the news of the Demon Race harming the Human Race

11:08.930 --> 11:10.360
by a day.

11:10.390 --> 11:11.000
Otherwise,

11:11.020 --> 11:11.940
the Demon Race wouldn't have had the chance

11:11.970 --> 11:13.240
to wreak havoc in Ning'an City.

11:13.270 --> 11:14.560
I heard that the person

11:14.580 --> 11:16.460
is the daughter of the governor of Ning'an City.

11:17.360 --> 11:18.690
Do you think Chong Zhao

11:18.720 --> 11:20.150
has fallen in love?

11:20.150 --> 11:22.740
He actually made such a huge mistake for a woman.

11:22.760 --> 11:23.670
Alright.

11:23.700 --> 11:25.340
The high-up Eternals are waiting.

11:25.360 --> 11:26.720
Let's take the elixirs back first.

11:27.000 --> 11:27.600
Master Turtle.

11:27.600 --> 11:28.510
-We're leaving.
-See you.

11:28.510 --> 11:29.510
Go ahead.

11:36.930 --> 11:38.450
What did they mean by 300 lashes?

11:38.480 --> 11:39.670
And what is the Heart-guarding Cliff?

12:04.690 --> 12:05.820
Master.

12:05.870 --> 12:08.420
Have you learned anything these days?

12:10.720 --> 12:12.880
Of all the hardships in the world, guarding the heart is the hardest.

12:13.650 --> 12:14.610
Master,

12:15.180 --> 12:16.510
my resolve

12:17.320 --> 12:18.600
seems to be wavering.

12:19.400 --> 12:21.880
The Eternals are also made of flesh and blood.

12:21.910 --> 12:23.600
On this long journey,

12:24.080 --> 12:25.790
confusion and doubt

12:25.810 --> 12:27.710
are natural things.

12:27.730 --> 12:29.730
The true self-cultivation

12:29.760 --> 12:31.430
is not in the mountains,

12:31.570 --> 12:33.300
but in the bustling world.

12:33.390 --> 12:34.630
Go down the mountain.

12:35.390 --> 12:37.300
Experience what you must experience,

12:37.320 --> 12:39.680
and bear what you must bear.

12:40.290 --> 12:42.170
Right and wrong,

12:42.200 --> 12:43.840
good and evil, cause and effect—

12:43.860 --> 12:44.860
in the end,

12:44.890 --> 12:46.560
you will find the answer.

12:47.630 --> 12:48.570
Master.

12:49.700 --> 12:51.510
Do you still think there is

12:51.540 --> 12:53.660
nothing suspicious about my parents' death?

12:56.880 --> 12:58.640
After your parents' incident,

12:58.670 --> 13:00.150
the entire Lanling Sect was mobilized

13:00.170 --> 13:02.020
and investigated for a whole year,

13:02.790 --> 13:05.390
but in the end, the result was the same.

13:08.750 --> 13:09.790
Chong Zhao,

13:10.080 --> 13:12.320
some things should be let go

13:12.340 --> 13:13.740
when it's time.

13:14.230 --> 13:15.440
Otherwise,

13:15.480 --> 13:17.320
you'll suffer.

13:29.120 --> 13:31.160
Recently, Cold Spring Palace has been very active.

13:31.180 --> 13:32.970
Within three months, they've wiped out three clans.

13:33.790 --> 13:35.980
Zhen Yu has taken the internal elixirs of the three chiefs

13:36.000 --> 13:37.830
to heal the wound from his severed tail.

13:37.860 --> 13:39.550
Being so impatient,

13:39.600 --> 13:41.190
he must be planning to stir up trouble again.

13:41.210 --> 13:42.520
With me here,

13:42.550 --> 13:44.200
Zhen Yu won't stir up any big trouble.

13:44.230 --> 13:45.830
What's the situation at Jingyou Mountain?

13:45.850 --> 13:47.560
The Jingyou Fox Clan has always stayed out of external conflicts.

13:47.590 --> 13:49.000
They didn't make any moves.

13:49.100 --> 13:50.840
The top priority now

13:50.990 --> 13:53.250
is still to help Bai Shuo gather the Five Contemplations.

13:53.370 --> 13:54.730
As for everything else, we can just watch from the sidelines.

13:55.330 --> 13:57.200
Master, I've been wanting to ask you a question.

13:57.220 --> 13:59.250
You compromised with Bai Shuo so many times.

13:59.280 --> 14:01.500
Is it really just because of the Desireless Stone?

14:01.610 --> 14:03.440
Master, I'm boldly reminding you.

14:03.550 --> 14:05.430
Don't let Bai Shuo become your weakness.

14:09.270 --> 14:11.150
Since the day I became the Demon King,

14:11.850 --> 14:13.200
I've had no weaknesses.

14:19.020 --> 14:20.510
Aren't you afraid of the Master punishing you?

14:20.510 --> 14:21.570
Whether you're an Eternal or a Demon,

14:21.600 --> 14:22.890
no matter how strong your sorcery is,

14:22.910 --> 14:24.640
once you fall in love,

14:24.670 --> 14:26.450
you'll have a weakness that can be exploited.

14:26.760 --> 14:27.710
Don't worry.

14:27.740 --> 14:28.790
Our Master

14:28.840 --> 14:30.200
will never fall in love.

14:30.230 --> 14:31.350
No matter what,

14:31.770 --> 14:33.980
if Bai Shuo causes any trouble in the future,

14:34.710 --> 14:36.380
even if it means risking the Master's punishment,

14:36.900 --> 14:38.730
I'll clear the obstacle.

14:46.820 --> 14:48.080
Are you still

14:48.080 --> 14:49.630
thinking about Chong Zhao?

14:53.400 --> 14:54.920
Don't drink too much.

14:54.940 --> 14:56.540
The peach blossom wine is rare.

14:56.570 --> 14:59.170
I've only kept a few bottles.

14:59.840 --> 15:01.120
Alright, alright.

15:01.390 --> 15:02.480
Keep going.

15:02.670 --> 15:04.790
You're my disciple after all.

15:04.790 --> 15:06.720
You can drink as much as my wine you want.

15:08.670 --> 15:09.670
Where is

15:10.100 --> 15:10.890
Heart-guarding Cliff?

15:10.920 --> 15:12.800
The Desireless Stone is still inside you.

15:12.820 --> 15:14.390
You can't run around.

15:14.420 --> 15:17.730
And Chong Zhao delayed reporting the demon situation because of you.

15:17.750 --> 15:19.590
If something happens to you in the Eternal Race,

15:19.630 --> 15:21.560
and he ends up clashing with the sect for you,

15:21.580 --> 15:22.770
what should we do?

15:22.790 --> 15:24.000
Because of me?

15:27.210 --> 15:28.570
For me,

15:30.220 --> 15:32.300
he almost got an entire city killed.

15:33.270 --> 15:35.550
If it hadn't been for the Five Eternals of Lanling arriving in time,

15:36.300 --> 15:38.730
and if my father hadn't sacrificed his life to exchange for Kindness,

15:40.180 --> 15:42.350
the whole city would have been destroyed.

15:43.510 --> 15:45.670
I honestly wish he had never done it for me.

15:46.600 --> 15:48.170
If the Five Eternals had arrived earlier,

15:49.540 --> 15:51.500
maybe the city wouldn't have fallen into chaos,

15:52.330 --> 15:54.280
and maybe my father wouldn't have...

15:55.230 --> 15:57.560
But what right do I have to blame him?

15:59.150 --> 16:00.500
After all,

16:00.870 --> 16:02.870
everything that happened in Ning'an City

16:04.800 --> 16:06.680
was because of me.

16:09.370 --> 16:10.460
Girl,

16:10.490 --> 16:12.250
there are many things in this world

16:12.270 --> 16:13.950
that can't be judged right or wrong.

16:13.980 --> 16:16.700
No one can foresee everything in the world.

16:16.720 --> 16:17.670
Most of the time,

16:17.700 --> 16:18.300
we just

16:18.320 --> 16:20.050
follow our hearts.

16:20.080 --> 16:21.800
The past cannot be changed.

16:21.840 --> 16:23.680
We must look forward.

16:24.950 --> 16:26.160
Yeah.

16:26.800 --> 16:28.280
I can't go back to the past.

16:32.140 --> 16:33.870
To the bright moon,

16:34.030 --> 16:35.290
to the night sky,

16:36.770 --> 16:38.920
to this miserable life,

16:40.130 --> 16:43.520
♫Don't linger, don't regret♫

16:41.070 --> 16:43.130
and to the past that I can't go back to.

16:43.420 --> 16:44.610
Cheers!

16:44.550 --> 16:46.910
♫The last moonlight♫

16:44.710 --> 16:46.240
You're still young!

16:46.260 --> 16:47.490
Why did you say that your life is miserable?

16:47.520 --> 16:49.090
Do you even know what life is?

16:47.940 --> 16:51.560
♫The water from my hometown flows gently♫

16:50.050 --> 16:51.680
Then tell me,

16:52.730 --> 16:55.360
♫Sending me to the distant place♫

16:52.790 --> 16:54.910
what is life?

16:56.050 --> 17:00.060
♫In this life, at this time♫

16:56.460 --> 16:58.890
I can't tell you

16:58.920 --> 17:00.560
what life is.

17:00.400 --> 17:03.870
♫I dare not look back♫

17:02.020 --> 17:03.380
But...

17:03.410 --> 17:05.369
if I must say,

17:04.650 --> 17:07.869
♫Is there the same moonlight♫

17:06.050 --> 17:07.180
life

17:07.200 --> 17:08.839
is the process of going from having nothing

17:09.050 --> 17:12.099
♫on your path?♫

17:09.290 --> 17:11.440
to having nothing again.

17:12.030 --> 17:14.400
The beginning and the end are already set.

17:12.930 --> 17:15.970
♫I'm walking on a never-ending long road♫

17:15.230 --> 17:17.230
But the experiences in between

17:16.500 --> 17:19.640
♫In the vast world, how can I go there?♫

17:17.250 --> 17:20.140
are up to you to decide.

17:20.170 --> 17:22.740
With my thousand years of age,

17:20.619 --> 17:22.480
♫The night wind is chaotic, and the sound of the Qin is broken♫

17:22.760 --> 17:25.210
I can tell you four things not to do:

17:23.130 --> 17:24.960
♫The moonlight is gentle♫

17:25.480 --> 17:28.200
♫All the attachments left are just a dream♫

17:25.750 --> 17:26.980
don't be obsessed,

17:27.000 --> 17:28.329
don't torment yourself,

17:28.359 --> 17:29.790
don't force things,

17:29.280 --> 17:32.330
♫I listen to the past, never enough♫

17:29.810 --> 17:31.240
and don't be pretentious.

17:31.470 --> 17:32.840
Live

17:32.500 --> 17:35.760
♫I sing until I have no voice, only wandering remains♫

17:32.860 --> 17:34.410
your life well.

17:35.410 --> 17:36.300
Understood?

17:36.450 --> 17:38.770
♫I forget the past, don't care anymore♫

17:39.170 --> 17:40.340
Girl,

17:39.500 --> 17:40.830
♫After many cycles♫

17:41.060 --> 17:42.510
I don't know

17:41.590 --> 17:46.220
♫I ended up with desolation♫

17:42.670 --> 17:45.260
how much you've really taken in.

17:45.450 --> 17:46.410
Fine.

17:47.150 --> 17:48.800
Everyone

17:48.960 --> 17:50.700
has to walk their own path.

17:50.800 --> 17:52.190
Whether it's good or bad,

17:52.460 --> 17:54.180
only by experiencing it yourself

17:54.980 --> 17:56.590
will you truly understand.

18:03.250 --> 18:03.410
[On the 22nd of June, in the 9th year of Chenghuai, my husband Chong Tai and I went to the Western Mountain]

18:03.430 --> 18:04.270
[On the 18th of June, in the 9th year of Chenghuai, my husband Chong Tai and I patrolled a remote area in the southern part of the city at night]

18:04.310 --> 18:05.260
[On the 11th of April, in the 9th year of Chenghuai, my husband Chong Tai and I patrolled the city]

18:16.230 --> 18:18.520
On the 7th of May, in the 9th year of Chenghuai,

18:18.540 --> 18:21.040
my husband Chong Tai and I were patrolling the southeast.

18:21.070 --> 18:22.620
We saw a village in the distance,

18:22.640 --> 18:23.850
with paths crisscrossing

18:23.880 --> 18:25.460
and people coming and going.

18:24.740 --> 18:26.920
[Chong Tai, Eternal, Lanling Sect]
[Meng Ning, Eternal, Lanling Sect]

18:25.610 --> 18:27.780
-Look.
-We wanted to enter the village to investigate,

18:27.920 --> 18:30.880
but when we stepped forward, the scene and the people suddenly vanished.

18:31.570 --> 18:34.590
Could this be the mirage in the legend?

18:40.550 --> 18:42.090
That's weird.

18:42.110 --> 18:42.910
Yes.

18:46.920 --> 18:49.210
On the 14th of June, in the 9th year of Chenghuai,

18:49.240 --> 18:52.400
my husband Chong Tai and I were passing through Qingyao Mountain

18:52.420 --> 18:55.000
when we saw a snake demon kill more than ten people.

18:55.020 --> 18:57.300
So we tried to kill the demon,

18:57.340 --> 19:00.060
but she was pregnant.

19:00.090 --> 19:02.950
In the end, we let the baby snakes return to the forests.

19:03.020 --> 19:04.460
I don't know whether what we did was right or wrong.

19:14.460 --> 19:15.950
All the Eternals know that your parents were killed

19:15.970 --> 19:18.100
by a scorpion demon ten years ago.

19:18.130 --> 19:19.210
But do you know

19:19.240 --> 19:21.090
that two days before your parents were killed,

19:21.110 --> 19:23.310
Qian Yin had already died?

19:23.340 --> 19:25.860
You've been investigating for years but have found nothing.

19:25.880 --> 19:27.230
Do you know why?

19:27.720 --> 19:28.800
Because

19:29.290 --> 19:31.440
you've never set foot in the Demon Race.

19:32.050 --> 19:33.810
What you see now

19:33.840 --> 19:35.390
may not be the truth.

19:35.420 --> 19:37.630
And in places you can't see,

19:37.650 --> 19:39.130
the truth

19:39.160 --> 19:40.640
might be right there.

19:45.800 --> 19:48.030
On the 15th of July, in the 9th year of Chenghuai,

19:48.100 --> 19:49.710
the Eternals and demons fought a great battle,

19:49.740 --> 19:51.590
and we lost more than half of our forces.

19:51.800 --> 19:53.660
While we were cleaning up the bodies of the Eternals,

19:53.850 --> 19:57.300
two of them showed no signs of demon injuries.

20:07.540 --> 20:09.170
Since they weren't killed by demons,

20:09.200 --> 20:11.050
how did they die?

20:11.280 --> 20:12.650
Did my parents uncover something

20:12.680 --> 20:14.270
that led to their deaths?

20:15.240 --> 20:16.000
It seems

20:16.810 --> 20:18.740
I really need to visit the Demon Race.

20:29.450 --> 20:31.020
You came after all.

20:36.700 --> 20:39.180
Why do you always want to get physical every time you see me?

20:39.200 --> 20:40.330
I do miss the you

20:40.360 --> 20:42.320
who saved me in Ning'an City.

20:42.340 --> 20:44.040
Don't even mention Ning'an City!

20:44.060 --> 20:46.020
Just the fact that you used the Nether Poison to harm the Human Race

20:46.050 --> 20:47.580
is enough for me to execute you right now!

20:48.080 --> 20:49.140
Is that so?

20:53.050 --> 20:55.680
So today, are you here in the Cold Spring Palace's territory

20:55.710 --> 20:57.190
to kill me

20:57.210 --> 20:58.870
or to beg me?

20:58.900 --> 21:00.600
Take me to see Qian Yin's grave.

21:40.090 --> 21:42.580
How dare you show disrespect to my guest?

21:45.240 --> 21:47.510
Sorry for startling you.

22:01.850 --> 22:03.300
Just like humans,

22:03.330 --> 22:04.490
demons who die

22:04.540 --> 22:06.300
would be buried by their family members,

22:06.330 --> 22:07.200
and monuments would be erected

22:07.220 --> 22:08.350
in their memory.

22:10.450 --> 22:11.210
That

22:11.240 --> 22:12.650
is Qian Yin's grave.

22:13.720 --> 22:15.850
He died on the 15th of July, ten years ago,

22:15.880 --> 22:16.670
and your parents

22:16.690 --> 22:18.180
died on the 17th of July.

22:32.760 --> 22:35.260
You expect me to believe you with just a tombstone inscription?

22:35.280 --> 22:37.200
You've come here with me.

22:37.230 --> 22:39.180
You still won't admit that you believe me?

22:43.680 --> 22:44.920
Ten years of Fortunei

22:44.920 --> 22:46.350
and seven years of wintergreen

22:46.370 --> 22:47.760
can be used to make a fourth-grade elixir,

22:47.790 --> 22:49.030
which can gather spiritual energy.

22:49.460 --> 22:50.790
Twenty years of withered Poria

22:50.810 --> 22:52.330
and thirty years of perilla leaves

22:52.350 --> 22:53.780
can be used to make a third-grade elixir,

22:53.800 --> 22:54.870
which can expand spiritual veins.

22:54.900 --> 22:57.140
A hundred years of refined ice and a thousand years of Snow Lotus

22:57.160 --> 22:58.270
can be used to make a second-grade elixir,

22:58.300 --> 22:59.510
which can refine spiritual foundations.

23:05.160 --> 23:06.160
Master,

23:06.180 --> 23:07.910
why is there no record of first-grade elixirs?

23:07.940 --> 23:08.940
First-grade elixirs?

23:08.960 --> 23:11.270
That's a legend from ancient times.

23:11.300 --> 23:13.000
No one has ever seen one.

23:15.530 --> 23:17.070
Tell me more about it.

23:17.090 --> 23:18.520
Maybe I can make it.

23:20.290 --> 23:22.440
I'm not underestimating you.

23:22.460 --> 23:23.490
A first-grade elixir can even

23:23.510 --> 23:26.600
withstand the thunder tribulation of a high-up Eternal ascending.

23:26.630 --> 23:27.800
It's not an ordinary thing.

23:27.860 --> 23:30.200
I've never made one myself.

23:30.320 --> 23:31.470
You?

23:31.490 --> 23:33.160
Forget it.

23:33.180 --> 23:34.660
If I really manage to make it,

23:34.690 --> 23:35.740
what will my reward be?

23:35.760 --> 23:36.840
You can't make it.

23:36.870 --> 23:38.660
Tell me what the reward will be first.

23:40.260 --> 23:43.140
How about you tell me what reward you want first?

23:43.160 --> 23:45.000
If I make it,

23:45.480 --> 23:47.330
lend me your turtle shell.

23:47.350 --> 23:48.980
The shell of a 1000-year-old Mystery Turtle

23:49.010 --> 23:50.100
can make divination more accurate.

23:50.130 --> 23:51.180
You want my shell?

23:51.210 --> 23:52.340
Don't even think about it.

23:52.360 --> 23:53.470
You're not after my shell,

23:53.510 --> 23:54.570
you're after my life.

23:54.590 --> 23:55.460
If a turtle loses its shell,

23:55.490 --> 23:56.900
it can be easily killed by anyone.

23:58.680 --> 23:59.610
Then where did this shell

23:59.680 --> 24:00.510
come from?

24:00.730 --> 24:02.120
It's the shell of a dead turtle.

24:02.680 --> 24:04.250
You gave me someone's remains?

24:04.570 --> 24:05.960
What's so strange about it?

24:05.980 --> 24:07.180
After I die,

24:07.210 --> 24:09.140
my remains

24:09.160 --> 24:10.820
will be yours too.

24:11.310 --> 24:13.240
How long will that take?

24:13.260 --> 24:15.060
You're really wishing for my death, aren't you?

24:16.320 --> 24:17.640
Of course not.

24:17.660 --> 24:19.390
I just think that a turtle like you

24:19.420 --> 24:20.770
might live longer than I will.

24:20.790 --> 24:21.640
I can't count on

24:21.680 --> 24:22.920
your remains.

24:22.940 --> 24:24.420
Good that you know.

24:27.730 --> 24:28.730
Where are you going?

24:28.760 --> 24:30.090
Going back to sleep.

24:30.110 --> 24:31.670
So you little troublemaker

24:31.720 --> 24:32.750
won't try to get my shell

24:32.770 --> 24:34.130
while I'm asleep.

24:45.610 --> 24:46.720
Now that Old Turtle has left,

24:46.750 --> 24:48.030
the long night

24:48.050 --> 24:49.420
does seem a bit boring.

24:53.920 --> 24:55.400
It's so late now.

24:55.430 --> 24:57.390
I wonder if that Demon King is asleep yet.

25:00.370 --> 25:01.330
Fan Yue?

25:07.890 --> 25:09.410
He really is asleep.

25:13.390 --> 25:14.330
What?

25:17.640 --> 25:18.570
Nothing.

25:18.600 --> 25:19.360
I'm staying up late

25:19.380 --> 25:20.490
making elixirs.

25:20.950 --> 25:22.060
So?

25:22.270 --> 25:23.270
So?

25:23.770 --> 25:25.830
Don't ask me like it's none of your business.

25:26.200 --> 25:27.920
It was supposed to be you teaching me.

25:28.130 --> 25:29.850
But you sent me to Old Turtle

25:29.880 --> 25:31.430
and now you're just sitting back,

25:31.450 --> 25:32.580
enjoying your free time.

25:32.610 --> 25:33.650
Enjoying my free time?

25:34.850 --> 25:35.770
What else would you be doing?

25:35.800 --> 25:36.800
What are you doing?

25:37.330 --> 25:38.760
Are you busy

25:38.790 --> 25:40.560
fighting over territory with the Cold Spring Palace?

25:46.080 --> 25:46.990
Fan Yue.

25:47.370 --> 25:48.460
I'm listening.

25:49.250 --> 25:50.380
Let me tell you,

25:50.630 --> 25:53.430
my alchemy skills are pretty good now.

25:53.850 --> 25:55.530
If I make a first-grade elixir,

25:55.560 --> 25:57.810
even Old Turtle will have to call me Master.

25:57.830 --> 25:59.660
It's said that first-grade elixirs are very powerful.

25:59.690 --> 26:00.970
Once I make one and take it,

26:00.990 --> 26:02.510
both Eternals and demons will be afraid of me.

26:02.840 --> 26:04.320
So will you.

26:04.840 --> 26:05.630
Really?

26:06.360 --> 26:07.530
Just you wait.

26:06.860 --> 26:10.630
♫We're destined to be together forever from the first sight♫

26:08.720 --> 26:11.000
I also learned some divination techniques from Old Turtle.

26:11.360 --> 26:12.730
But I'm not used to

26:11.490 --> 26:13.370
♫Goodbye, loneliness♫

26:12.760 --> 26:14.280
this turtle shell,

26:14.450 --> 26:17.920
♫The one who was slightly late♫

26:14.890 --> 26:16.120
so I haven't been able to get any predictions.

26:16.780 --> 26:18.820
Do you think he's deceiving me?

26:18.850 --> 26:20.440
Deceiving you?

26:19.200 --> 26:25.530
♫You came towards me, closer and closer♫

26:20.460 --> 26:21.590
He's a 1000-year-old turtle.

26:21.620 --> 26:22.770
He's really cunning.

26:25.570 --> 26:26.800
There's a moon here,

26:26.820 --> 26:27.660
a crescent moon.

26:27.390 --> 26:34.150
♫You enriched my life♫

26:27.680 --> 26:28.720
Is there one over there?

26:32.040 --> 26:33.610
So, both the Eternals and demons

26:33.640 --> 26:35.460
are looking at the same moon.

26:34.710 --> 26:38.240
♫The stars light up your eyes♫

26:35.550 --> 26:37.380
All the races live on the same land.

26:38.030 --> 26:40.310
Naturally, they see the same moon.

26:42.480 --> 26:45.730
♫You are the light I yearn for♫

26:42.930 --> 26:45.380
You talked a lot today.

26:45.410 --> 26:46.770
What exactly are you trying to say?

26:46.600 --> 26:51.190
♫You are my determined way home♫

26:46.790 --> 26:48.510
Didn't I tell you?

26:49.380 --> 26:51.420
Staying up late making elixirs is very boring.

26:51.450 --> 26:52.340
Boring?

26:51.610 --> 26:56.920
♫Let this moment stay forever♫

26:54.010 --> 26:55.960
Am I just your entertainment?

26:56.040 --> 26:57.760
Not really.

26:57.780 --> 26:59.590
It's just that when I'm bored,

26:58.020 --> 27:01.480
♫I'm hugging you in the crowd♫

26:59.640 --> 27:01.070
I naturally think of a boring person.

27:01.110 --> 27:02.110
Bai Shuo.

27:02.110 --> 27:03.480
I have things to do. I have to go.

27:02.270 --> 27:04.240
♫Let's never let go♫

27:13.270 --> 27:14.070
Master.

27:14.100 --> 27:14.970
Master.

27:17.320 --> 27:18.600
Why are there still so many?

27:18.620 --> 27:20.140
Previously, when you went to Ning'an City,

27:20.170 --> 27:21.630
matters piled up in the Polar Region.

27:21.660 --> 27:23.310
Everyone is waiting for you to make decisions.

27:27.060 --> 27:28.260
Then why

27:28.290 --> 27:30.250
were even trivial matters like disputes

27:30.270 --> 27:31.640
presented to me?

27:32.350 --> 27:33.710
There's no choice.

27:33.810 --> 27:34.770
Among the ten thousand demons in the Polar Region,

27:34.800 --> 27:36.280
no one respects anyone else.

27:36.300 --> 27:37.860
The only one they respect is you, the Master.

27:37.890 --> 27:39.560
If you don't decide the outcome or make a ruling,

27:39.590 --> 27:41.300
they'll keep fighting forever.

27:41.320 --> 27:42.250
So, Master,

27:42.270 --> 27:43.230
please bear with it

27:43.260 --> 27:44.350
and finish reading these files.

27:45.430 --> 27:46.470
Wait.

27:48.620 --> 27:50.140
What can I do for you?

27:50.170 --> 27:51.490
I have a question.

27:51.510 --> 27:53.550
What do you think of when you're bored?

27:53.570 --> 27:55.090
When I'm bored?

27:55.120 --> 27:57.150
Drinking, fighting and sleeping.

27:57.190 --> 27:58.560
I mean, what person do you think of?

28:02.130 --> 28:03.290
I do think of someone.

28:03.320 --> 28:04.120
Who is it?

28:04.810 --> 28:06.430
Can I not tell you?

28:06.660 --> 28:07.620
Why?

28:09.200 --> 28:11.400
I'm embarrassed to tell you the person I like.

28:11.420 --> 28:12.180
Master, I'll leave you to your work.

28:12.210 --> 28:13.250
I'll put these over there for you.

28:19.270 --> 28:20.750
The person she likes?

28:25.610 --> 28:26.540
You killed him?

28:27.650 --> 28:28.490
Yes.

28:28.810 --> 28:30.880
Zhong Zhao trespassed into the Cold Spring Palace's territory.

28:30.910 --> 28:33.190
Lady Fu Ling, not only didn't you capture him,

28:33.210 --> 28:34.730
but you also killed one of your own.

28:35.530 --> 28:37.380
What exactly are you planning to do?

28:38.180 --> 28:39.850
I'm getting more and more confused.

28:39.870 --> 28:41.300
I don't need you to understand.

28:41.840 --> 28:42.760
What?

28:42.780 --> 28:44.580
Is the life of the bear demon not worth anything?

28:44.610 --> 28:45.970
Or is it that

28:46.000 --> 28:47.590
in your heart,

28:47.640 --> 28:49.540
you only care about Chong Zhao's life?

28:50.500 --> 28:53.080
When you used little demons to practice,

28:53.180 --> 28:55.100
did you ever care about their lives?

28:55.130 --> 28:56.170
Besides,

28:56.190 --> 28:58.220
this bear demon almost ruined my plan.

28:58.270 --> 28:59.420
He deserved to die.

28:59.440 --> 29:00.710
For such a trivial matter,

29:00.750 --> 29:02.970
you actually came to report to the Grand Master.

29:02.990 --> 29:05.080
I really underestimated how petty you are.

29:05.420 --> 29:06.260
Enough.

29:06.530 --> 29:07.400
Are you done?

29:08.330 --> 29:09.170
Fu Ling,

29:09.610 --> 29:10.920
tell me about your plan.

29:10.940 --> 29:12.350
Grand Master, you once taught us

29:12.380 --> 29:13.670
that when someone wants something,

29:13.690 --> 29:15.010
we should give it to them.

29:15.040 --> 29:16.090
Even if it's fake,

29:16.110 --> 29:17.680
it must be convincing.

29:17.710 --> 29:19.880
Chong Zhao is investigating the truth behind his parents' deaths,

29:19.900 --> 29:21.300
but he has no leads.

29:21.330 --> 29:23.530
At this point, if I give him a clue—

29:23.550 --> 29:25.220
whether it's real or not—

29:25.250 --> 29:26.890
he will cling to it.

29:26.920 --> 29:28.240
As long as he wants to investigate,

29:28.260 --> 29:29.940
he will have no choice

29:29.970 --> 29:31.010
but to fall into my trap.

29:31.030 --> 29:31.990
Lady Fu Ling,

29:32.030 --> 29:34.000
you truly are a master of strategy.

29:34.490 --> 29:36.200
But don't say I didn't remind you.

29:36.220 --> 29:37.650
You'd better settle this quickly

29:37.680 --> 29:39.160
to avoid future complications.

29:39.620 --> 29:41.180
And don't let any other thoughts take root,

29:41.750 --> 29:44.550
or you might disgrace your identity as the Young Lord of Cold Spring Palace.

29:47.210 --> 29:48.210
Alright.

29:48.640 --> 29:49.430
Since

29:49.960 --> 29:51.550
he has an obsession he can't let go of,

29:51.550 --> 29:53.690
we'll help him strengthen it.

29:54.420 --> 29:55.900
Once he has an inner demon,

29:55.930 --> 29:56.900
he will

29:56.930 --> 29:59.170
be of use to the Cold Spring Palace.

29:59.190 --> 30:00.150
Fu Ling,

30:00.200 --> 30:01.110
I want you

30:01.110 --> 30:03.050
to use every means possible

30:03.080 --> 30:05.160
to force him to abandon being an Eternal, become a demon,

30:05.790 --> 30:06.590
and join

30:06.610 --> 30:07.800
our Cold Spring Palace.

30:08.470 --> 30:09.470
Yes.

30:23.130 --> 30:24.240
Master!

30:24.260 --> 30:25.260
Master!

30:26.200 --> 30:27.000
What happened?

30:27.030 --> 30:27.800
Did

30:27.820 --> 30:29.340
the alchemy furnace explode again?

30:29.370 --> 30:30.270
I made it!

30:40.550 --> 30:42.630
Not bad, my disciple.

30:42.650 --> 30:45.280
You can make a second-grade elixir already!

30:46.480 --> 30:48.560
I didn't misjudge you after all.

30:48.580 --> 30:50.300
This time,

30:50.340 --> 30:52.140
I can give Fan Yue a report.

30:52.170 --> 30:53.810
Why should you report to him?

30:56.400 --> 30:58.330
If she fails to learn anything,

30:58.360 --> 31:01.120
I'll strip you of your 1000-year-old turtle shell.

31:04.540 --> 31:06.310
Luckily, your comprehension is exceptional.

31:06.310 --> 31:08.480
It looks like my 1000-year-old turtle shell is safe now.

31:09.030 --> 31:10.440
Today is a good day.

31:10.440 --> 31:12.600
I'll go and get a couple of bottles...

31:12.640 --> 31:13.720
of nectar.

31:13.720 --> 31:15.750
Let's celebrate.

31:15.750 --> 31:17.030
Again?

31:17.030 --> 31:17.790
Yes!

31:31.670 --> 31:32.960
Didn't you go to get the nectar?

31:32.960 --> 31:34.570
How did you come back so quickly?

31:38.920 --> 31:39.770
Bai Shuo?

31:39.820 --> 31:40.790
It's you?

31:41.790 --> 31:43.580
You escaped from the Demon Race?

31:44.140 --> 31:45.760
Are you here to seek help from our Eternal Race?

31:46.340 --> 31:47.270
No, wait.

31:47.890 --> 31:48.640
You are a human.

31:48.640 --> 31:50.360
How did you enter the Eternal Sect?

31:50.790 --> 31:53.160
And why are you hiding here with Old Turtle?

31:55.550 --> 31:56.340
Tell me!

31:56.870 --> 31:58.570
What happened?

32:03.000 --> 32:04.960
Sir, you sure have a big temper.

32:04.980 --> 32:06.500
You just saw me, and now you want to get physical already.

32:06.530 --> 32:08.250
That day, you were kidnapped by Master Bright Moon.

32:08.270 --> 32:10.640
The Eternal Sect sent countless disciples to search for you in the Polar Region.

32:11.040 --> 32:13.290
Now that you've appeared in the Eternal Sect,

32:13.560 --> 32:14.820
come with me to meet the Sect Leade!

32:15.410 --> 32:17.210
You're not looking for me.

32:17.240 --> 32:18.130
You're looking for the Desireless Stone.

32:18.150 --> 32:19.770
The Desireless Stone belongs to the Eternals!

32:19.790 --> 32:20.640
It should stay in Lanling!

32:20.640 --> 32:22.030
But I don't belong to the Eternals.

32:22.030 --> 32:23.110
It makes no difference!

32:30.790 --> 32:32.440
You're carrying a demonic object.

32:32.820 --> 32:34.380
Who are you trying to send a message to?

32:35.310 --> 32:38.000
Is it Master Bright Moon?

32:38.030 --> 32:39.920
I've always said that humans are hard to predict,

32:39.940 --> 32:41.760
and they're easily controlled by demons.

32:41.790 --> 32:43.660
You're a human carrying the Desireless Stone.

32:43.680 --> 32:45.360
Don't even think about leaving!

32:55.440 --> 32:56.200
Chong Zhao!

32:56.230 --> 32:57.150
Get out of my way!

32:57.170 --> 32:58.170
Bai Shuo is innocent.

32:58.200 --> 32:59.570
Uncle Master, you can't kill her!

32:59.590 --> 33:00.400
Shut up!

33:00.430 --> 33:01.880
Don't forget who you are.

33:01.900 --> 33:03.210
She carries the Desireless Stone

33:03.240 --> 33:04.320
and is colluding with the Demon Race.

33:04.350 --> 33:06.310
She is an enemy to our entire Eternal Race!

33:06.310 --> 33:07.840
Don't be so blind!

33:07.870 --> 33:09.590
I'm not the one who's blind.

33:09.620 --> 33:10.860
You are!

33:10.880 --> 33:12.730
Are you saying I'm blind to right and wrong?

33:12.760 --> 33:14.260
I dare not disobey you.

33:14.290 --> 33:15.940
But if you insist on this,

33:16.010 --> 33:17.610
I will have no choice but to go against you!

33:17.960 --> 33:18.880
You are beyond help!

33:18.880 --> 33:19.750
Enough!

33:22.990 --> 33:23.890
Chong Zhao,

33:25.170 --> 33:26.570
this has nothing to do with you.

33:30.100 --> 33:31.730
Entering the Demon Palace that day

33:31.760 --> 33:33.360
was my own choice.

33:34.100 --> 33:36.520
Just like now, I choose not to stay with the Eternals.

33:40.060 --> 33:41.660
As an Eternal, you want to kill a human.

33:41.690 --> 33:43.170
As long as you're at peace with it,

33:43.190 --> 33:44.320
go ahead.

33:46.920 --> 33:47.810
Stop.

33:47.830 --> 33:49.350
Sect Leader, you came at just the right time.

33:49.380 --> 33:50.340
Bai Shuo is colluding with the Demon Race

33:50.360 --> 33:52.030
and sneaked into Lanling. Her intentions must be malicious.

33:52.060 --> 33:53.300
She must be eliminated!

33:53.530 --> 33:55.670
Sect Leader, are you going to kill me too?

33:55.770 --> 33:58.580
Lanling Sect will not kill an innocent person.

33:58.610 --> 34:00.890
I know you didn't do anything wrong.

34:01.950 --> 34:03.360
So, are you willing to let me go?

34:03.380 --> 34:05.010
Of course,

34:05.040 --> 34:06.480
that's impossible.

34:07.890 --> 34:10.860
The Desireless Stone concerns the peace of the world.

34:11.020 --> 34:12.920
As the Sect Leader of Lanling,

34:12.960 --> 34:16.230
I can never allow it to fall into the hands of the demons.

34:16.230 --> 34:16.920
Master!

34:23.969 --> 34:25.489
What do you want?

34:25.659 --> 34:27.909
Rather than letting you return to the Demon Race,

34:28.840 --> 34:30.170
it's better to...

34:30.800 --> 34:32.469
make you forget it.

34:49.510 --> 34:51.400
West sun mountain.

34:51.429 --> 34:53.310
East moon river.

34:53.360 --> 34:56.409
A snake slithers across the grass.

34:56.460 --> 34:59.310
A fish leaps above the sandy sea.

34:59.330 --> 35:02.120
The earth knows, but the sky does not.

35:02.150 --> 35:04.720
Only by stepping in can you find the way.

35:21.790 --> 35:22.710
The head of the Eternal Sect

35:22.710 --> 35:24.430
actually laid hands on a human.

35:24.460 --> 35:25.310
I think

35:25.330 --> 35:26.250
Lanling Sect

35:26.280 --> 35:28.150
should just change its name to Lanling Evil Sect.

35:28.170 --> 35:28.900
Fan Yue!

35:29.230 --> 35:30.860
How dare you break into our Eternal Sect?

35:30.890 --> 35:32.480
Give us Bai Shuo!

35:34.080 --> 35:35.650
I'm here to take you back.

35:36.560 --> 35:37.720
Shuo!

35:38.040 --> 35:39.630
You can't go back to the Demon Race with him!

35:39.660 --> 35:40.930
Fan Yue,

35:41.170 --> 35:44.560
are you really going to go against the entire Eternal Sect?

35:44.590 --> 35:46.500
Bai Shuo is mine.

35:46.520 --> 35:48.770
I allowed her to stay temporarily in the Eternal Sect,

35:48.790 --> 35:51.500
but that doesn't mean Lanling Sect has the right to keep her here.

35:58.260 --> 35:59.140
Sect Leader,

35:59.170 --> 36:00.290
that turtle shell...

36:00.680 --> 36:01.950
It looks familiar.

36:02.550 --> 36:04.760
So familiar.

36:09.440 --> 36:11.890
Sect Leader, I'm innocent!

36:11.960 --> 36:15.400
I was forced by Fan Yue to become Bai Shuo's teacher

36:15.400 --> 36:17.670
for a few days as a way of repaying his favor.

36:17.670 --> 36:18.760
The fact that the Desireless Stone was stolen

36:18.760 --> 36:21.480
has nothing to do with me!

36:21.480 --> 36:22.540
Stop making excuses.

36:22.570 --> 36:24.980
If you hadn't given him the turtle shell,

36:25.080 --> 36:29.090
how could he have broken into our Lanling Sect?

36:29.880 --> 36:31.280
When I gave him the shell to repay his kindness,

36:31.310 --> 36:32.580
I didn't know he was the Demon King.

36:32.600 --> 36:33.520
Your words alone aren't enough to prove it!

36:36.890 --> 36:37.770
Sect Leader,

36:37.800 --> 36:40.360
I'm utterly loyal to Lanling.

36:40.400 --> 36:41.710
Heaven and Earth are my witness.

36:41.710 --> 36:43.020
I didn't betray you!

36:43.070 --> 36:45.320
Please, spare me!

36:45.360 --> 36:46.560
Master,

36:46.580 --> 36:48.230
Old Turtle has been making elixirs for the Eternals for many years.

36:48.260 --> 36:49.900
This time, he was forced by Fan Yue.

36:50.160 --> 36:51.690
Master, please forgive him.

36:52.390 --> 36:54.640
You have no right to plead for Old Turtle!

36:54.660 --> 36:56.130
You dared to attack your teacher,

36:56.160 --> 36:58.440
and you even said I can't tell right from wrong.

36:58.460 --> 37:00.660
It seems the 300 lashes weren't enough for you!

37:00.710 --> 37:02.150
You need a few more!

37:02.180 --> 37:04.180
I didn't mean to offend you.

37:04.200 --> 37:06.150
But if you try to kill Bai Shuo,

37:06.180 --> 37:07.970
I can't just stand by and watch.

37:07.990 --> 37:09.160
I believe

37:09.190 --> 37:11.100
killing innocent people is not something the Eternals should do.

37:11.120 --> 37:12.160
Sect Leader, did you hear that?

37:12.190 --> 37:13.900
He said I kill innocent people!

37:14.680 --> 37:15.990
Alright, Jing Lei.

37:16.020 --> 37:18.140
Stop making things difficult for Chong Zhao.

37:18.190 --> 37:19.920
We've watched him grow up.

37:19.920 --> 37:21.190
We know him very well.

37:21.190 --> 37:23.240
As for Old Turtle…

37:23.730 --> 37:24.680
Lanling

37:24.710 --> 37:25.710
has been using

37:25.710 --> 37:27.290
the black turtle as our totem.

37:27.390 --> 37:28.710
If we really punish him,

37:28.710 --> 37:29.360
we'll become

37:29.360 --> 37:30.760
the laughingstock of the 72 Sects.

37:30.760 --> 37:32.110
So, I'm the bad guy now?

37:32.110 --> 37:33.070
Are you saying we won't punish either of them?

37:33.070 --> 37:33.920
Then tell me, what should we do?

37:33.920 --> 37:35.590
Calm down.

37:36.880 --> 37:37.760
Keep your voice down.

37:37.760 --> 37:39.900
You're about to burst my eardrums.

37:40.480 --> 37:41.480
Old Turtle,

37:41.880 --> 37:43.280
let me ask you.

37:43.280 --> 37:44.720
Since Fan Yue

37:44.750 --> 37:47.910
was able to use your turtle shell to enter our Lanling,

37:48.000 --> 37:50.550
can we use the same shell

37:50.580 --> 37:51.980
to find the Bright Moon Palace?

37:53.430 --> 37:54.590
I've sensed it.

37:54.610 --> 37:55.340
Fan Yue has already

37:55.370 --> 37:57.210
destroyed the teleportation turtle shell he gave me.

37:57.230 --> 37:58.870
Now, no one can pass through.

37:58.920 --> 38:00.040
You contacted our enemies

38:00.060 --> 38:01.270
and leaked our techniques.

38:01.320 --> 38:02.320
What's the use of keeping you?

38:02.320 --> 38:03.760
He's not entirely useless.

38:03.850 --> 38:05.080
Old Turtle's alchemy skills

38:05.110 --> 38:06.880
are considered one of the unique arts of us Eternals.

38:06.900 --> 38:07.940
The elixirs he makes,

38:07.970 --> 38:09.450
if sold to the villages down the mountain,

38:09.480 --> 38:10.930
could bring us some more money.

38:10.990 --> 38:12.800
You want to spare him for just a little money?

38:12.820 --> 38:14.260
A little money?

38:14.290 --> 38:15.480
Senior Jing Lei,

38:15.510 --> 38:17.340
why don't you make some money and show me?

38:17.370 --> 38:18.050
Okay!

38:18.070 --> 38:18.880
Sell it!

38:18.910 --> 38:19.500
Give it to her!

38:19.520 --> 38:20.370
Give it to her!

38:20.400 --> 38:21.110
Give it to her!

38:21.150 --> 38:22.670
-Give it to her!
-Stop it!

38:22.670 --> 38:23.440
Listen to me! Give it to her!

38:23.440 --> 38:24.440
Stop it!

38:24.440 --> 38:26.070
-Shut up!
-Shut up!

38:27.480 --> 38:28.650
Old Turtle,

38:28.680 --> 38:29.960
how about this?

38:30.520 --> 38:32.200
You've been in the sect for years.

38:32.230 --> 38:33.410
You haven't made any significant contributions,

38:33.920 --> 38:35.440
nor have you put in much effort.

38:36.330 --> 38:37.640
You'll be punished

38:37.660 --> 38:39.760
by making 100 more Great Restoration Elixirs every month.

38:39.790 --> 38:41.750
The money from selling them will be used to support the sect.

38:41.770 --> 38:42.850
That's all for now.

38:42.880 --> 38:43.750
100 elixirs?

38:43.780 --> 38:46.640
Doesn't that mean I'll be worked to death?

38:47.310 --> 38:48.960
You're reluctant, aren't you?

38:48.980 --> 38:49.900
In that case,

38:49.930 --> 38:51.220
we'll have to strip off your turtle shell,

38:51.240 --> 38:52.250
break your spiritual bone,

38:52.270 --> 38:53.070
and then...

38:53.910 --> 38:55.160
Say no more.

38:55.180 --> 38:55.930
I'm willing.

38:55.960 --> 38:57.120
I'm willing.

38:57.140 --> 38:58.710
Go!

39:03.130 --> 39:04.180
Sect Leader,

39:04.210 --> 39:05.600
Bai Shuo can activate the Desireless Stone,

39:05.620 --> 39:07.080
and she doesn't align with the Eternals.

39:07.110 --> 39:08.500
Please give the order,

39:08.520 --> 39:10.240
and I'll immediately lead the troops to the Demon Race

39:10.260 --> 39:11.220
and bring Bai Shuo back.

39:11.880 --> 39:13.440
I also request to go.

39:13.470 --> 39:15.010
Last time, we sent disciples

39:15.030 --> 39:16.970
to investigate the location of the Bright Moon Palace,

39:17.000 --> 39:19.220
but we still haven't made any progress.

39:19.640 --> 39:21.330
This Fan Yue,

39:21.380 --> 39:23.150
relying on the fact that the Eternal Race can't find him,

39:23.180 --> 39:24.370
is too arrogant.

39:24.960 --> 39:27.810
Is Fan Yue only relying on the fact that the Eternal Race can't find him?

39:27.840 --> 39:29.590
There are only a few of us here.

39:29.610 --> 39:31.180
Let's face the truth.

39:31.210 --> 39:34.020
Even if we find the Bright Moon Palace,

39:34.040 --> 39:35.780
we still won't be able to get Bai Shuo back.

39:36.140 --> 39:37.530
-Feng Yu.
-You…

39:37.560 --> 39:39.040
Can you stop always discouraging everyone?

39:39.110 --> 39:40.110
You should encourage us more.

39:40.150 --> 39:42.000
I'm just telling the truth.

39:42.030 --> 39:43.200
It's better than you guys

39:43.220 --> 39:44.130
deceiving yourselves.

39:44.160 --> 39:45.330
Come on, you...

39:45.360 --> 39:46.270
Alright.

39:46.290 --> 39:48.480
Feng Yu was right.

39:48.510 --> 39:51.270
The key to this matter is not Fan Yue,

39:51.290 --> 39:53.120
but Bai Shuo herself.

39:54.080 --> 39:55.960
Alright, dismiss.

39:55.990 --> 39:56.880
Well, Sect Leader...

39:56.900 --> 39:58.220
Dismiss.

39:58.250 --> 39:59.200
Fine.

40:08.540 --> 40:10.270
What else do you want to say?

40:10.290 --> 40:11.790
I feel like

40:12.030 --> 40:13.230
you're deliberately avoiding

40:13.250 --> 40:15.170
bringing back Bai Shuo and the Desireless Stone.

40:36.920 --> 40:39.850
I, Jin Yao, the 68th Sect Leader of Lanling,

40:39.880 --> 40:41.720
am here to respectfully hear the ancestral teachings of the sect.

40:52.920 --> 40:54.830
Lanling Sect Leader, listen to the order.

40:55.070 --> 40:57.880
The Desireless Stone will be awakened by a human girl.

40:57.990 --> 41:00.990
She is the only one in this world who can activate the divine stone.

41:01.160 --> 41:02.550
If she appears,

41:02.570 --> 41:04.930
Lanling must assist her in activating the Desireless Stone.

41:04.960 --> 41:06.330
This divine decree

41:06.370 --> 41:07.750
is known only

41:07.850 --> 41:09.290
to the Sect Leaders of Lanling.

41:09.310 --> 41:11.670
I will obey the divine decree.

41:16.510 --> 41:17.800
The ancestral teachings of Lanling

41:17.800 --> 41:19.550
have been passed down for tens of thousands of years.

41:19.710 --> 41:20.840
We have been waiting for the human girl

41:20.840 --> 41:23.940
who can activate the Desireless Stone.

41:24.250 --> 41:25.440
Now that

41:25.460 --> 41:28.340
Bai Shuo can awaken the Desireless Stone,

41:28.470 --> 41:31.110
she must be the fated one

41:31.140 --> 41:32.880
in the divine decree.

41:38.290 --> 41:40.270
Isn't this Wutong Heart Flame?

41:40.410 --> 41:42.660
Could the next Contemplation appear in Yi City?

41:42.680 --> 41:44.310
Wutong Heart Flame?

41:44.420 --> 41:45.530
Yi City?

41:45.610 --> 41:47.620
Wutong Heart Flame only appears in Yi City.

41:47.850 --> 41:48.820
And Yi City

41:48.880 --> 41:50.590
is where the Yi Clan lives.

41:50.610 --> 41:51.820
Yi Clan?

41:51.850 --> 41:53.330
I've never heard of it.

41:55.930 --> 41:57.340
Yi Clan is naturally strong,

41:57.370 --> 41:58.300
with incredible strength.

41:58.320 --> 41:59.470
However, due to their limited bloodline,

41:59.500 --> 42:00.620
their cultivation is mediocre.

42:00.640 --> 42:01.410
No matter how hard they try,

42:01.440 --> 42:03.530
they can only cultivate the lowest-level magic.

42:03.560 --> 42:05.250
They have always been discriminated against by the Eternals and demons,

42:05.270 --> 42:06.950
so they live far away in Yi City.

42:07.000 --> 42:07.960
Then what are we waiting for?

42:07.980 --> 42:08.900
Let's depart immediately.

42:09.380 --> 42:10.340
Yi City

42:10.880 --> 42:12.390
is a moving city in the desert,

42:12.410 --> 42:13.810
with its location constantly shifting.

42:13.840 --> 42:15.150
It is usually invisible and impossible to find.

42:15.990 --> 42:17.680
It only opens during the annual

42:17.710 --> 42:18.750
Wutong Martial Arts Contest,

42:18.770 --> 42:20.520
and only on that day

42:20.590 --> 42:22.870
can everyone know its exact location.

42:22.900 --> 42:24.060
So mysterious?

42:24.810 --> 42:27.130
What is Wutong Martial Arts Contest?

42:27.160 --> 42:29.230
A thousand years ago, the Eternal Race and Demon Race

42:29.280 --> 42:31.260
fought endlessly, battling over territories with heavy casualties.

42:31.330 --> 42:32.680
So, the Eternal Lord and Demon King at the time

42:32.710 --> 42:33.630
proposed that the two races

42:33.630 --> 42:35.820
hold an annual martial arts contest to settle their territorial disputes.

42:35.840 --> 42:36.960
The King of Yi,

42:37.000 --> 42:38.620
wanting to reconcile with the Eternals and demons,

42:38.640 --> 42:40.690
agreed to host the contest in Yi City,

42:40.720 --> 42:42.590
with three spirit pills made from Wutong Heart Flame

42:42.630 --> 42:43.940
as the prize for the winner.

42:43.960 --> 42:44.930
Wutong Spirit Pill

42:44.960 --> 42:46.510
is an extremely pure and sacred treasure.

42:46.550 --> 42:47.320
Those who use it

42:47.340 --> 42:48.570
can greatly increase their spiritual power

42:48.600 --> 42:49.600
and improve their cultivation.

42:50.080 --> 42:51.810
In the Desireless Stone, I foresaw

42:51.840 --> 42:53.840
many disciples from both the Eternal Race and Demon Race gathering in Yi City.

42:53.860 --> 42:55.340
It seems they are preparing for the second Contemplation.

42:55.370 --> 42:57.360
We not only need to enter Yi City,

42:57.380 --> 42:58.790
but we also have to hold the Wutong Martial Arts Contest,

42:58.820 --> 43:00.140
allowing disciples from both races

43:00.160 --> 43:01.640
to enter the city as well.

43:01.670 --> 43:04.370
It has been seven years since Yi City last held the Wutong Martial Arts Contest.

43:04.580 --> 43:06.120
Why has it suddenly stopped?

43:06.310 --> 43:08.480
Could something have happened in Yi City?

43:10.790 --> 43:12.310
Why do you have so many questions?

43:12.340 --> 43:14.730
I'm not only doing this for myself;

43:14.750 --> 43:16.140
it's also to help your Master.

43:16.170 --> 43:17.820
Are you still going to keep things from me?

43:18.170 --> 43:19.960
No one is keeping anything.

43:19.990 --> 43:22.160
No one knows why Yi City is closed,

43:22.180 --> 43:23.570
nor does anyone know

43:23.600 --> 43:24.560
where Yi City is now.

43:25.620 --> 43:26.970
You just said

43:27.000 --> 43:29.600
Yi City is a moving city in the desert?

43:29.620 --> 43:30.420
That's right.

43:31.080 --> 43:32.560
What if I tell you

43:32.590 --> 43:34.110
I might know where it is?

43:34.690 --> 43:36.090
How could you possibly know?

43:36.170 --> 43:37.770
The Desireless Stone showed me

43:37.790 --> 43:39.100
a desert

43:39.130 --> 43:40.450
and a children's rhyme.

43:41.480 --> 43:44.330
Not everything in this world can be explained

43:44.350 --> 43:45.940
or answered clearly.

43:45.970 --> 43:46.970
I'm doing this

43:46.990 --> 43:48.720
for my reasons.

43:49.290 --> 43:50.250
Chong Zhao,

43:50.280 --> 43:51.840
do you trust me?

43:51.860 --> 43:53.340
Of course I do.

43:53.960 --> 43:55.320
But Shuo is with the Demon Race.

43:56.150 --> 43:57.150
I'm worried about her.

43:57.180 --> 43:58.300
Don't worry.

43:58.320 --> 43:59.070
Master Bright Moon

43:59.100 --> 44:01.810
needs her to activate the Desireless Stone.

44:02.080 --> 44:03.810
He won't harm her for now.

44:04.350 --> 44:05.320
All we need to do now

44:05.320 --> 44:07.400
is wait for the right opportunity.

44:07.400 --> 44:08.440
Do you understand?

44:11.080 --> 44:13.400
You seem troubled.

44:13.620 --> 44:15.100
Is there something else?

44:16.360 --> 44:17.450
Master,

44:18.190 --> 44:20.050
I found Qian Yin's tombstone.
